  "reference_number": "RUS1619",
  "remarks": "\nAnton Viktorovich KOLTSOV is the so-called “Head” of the Russian-installed administration in temporarily controlled territory of Zaporizhzhia region, southern Ukraine. As a result of this, KOLTSOV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he is or has engaged in, and/or provided support for, policies or actions which destabilise Ukraine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
